1. *Posada* je ušla u avion i spremila se za poletanje. (*Posada* - The crew entered the plane and prepared for takeoff.)
2. Naša *posada* je veoma iskusna i pouzdana. (Our *posada* is very experienced and reliable.)
3. *Posadi* se za sto, molim te. (*Posadi* - Please, take a seat at the table.)
4. Moramo *posaditi* nove sadnice ovog proljeća. (*Posaditi* - We have to plant new seedlings this spring.)
5. Koje su tvoje odgovornosti kao člana *posade* broda? (What are your responsibilities as a member of the *posada* of the ship?)
6. Neki putnici su se žalili na ponašanje *posade* tokom leta. (Some passengers complained about the behavior of the *posada* during the flight.)
7. *Posade* su se smjenjivale na svaka tri sata tokom plovidbe. (*Posade* - The crews were changing every three hours during the voyage.)
8. Naša firma ima nekoliko *posada* koje su specijalizovane za različite vrste građevinskih radova. (Our company has several *posada* that specialize in different types of construction work.)